{"recipient_email":"{{node_prepare_context.recipient_email}}","subject":"","preview_text":"","body":"","pain_point":"","offer":"","call_to_action":"","tone":"professional_warm","followup_days":3,"confidence_score":0}

Rules:
- body must be the exact message the lead will receive.
- body must be plain text, no HTML, no logo, no fancy design, no placeholders.
